  "text": "negative dyadic strain represents appraisals of the difficulty of being in a family care relationship, positive dyadic interactions represent appraisals of the improved closeness and other gains associated with the care situation. Rather than representing opposing ends of the same continuum, these two appraisals can exist simultaneously (e.g. high dyadic strain in combination with high positive dyadic interactions) [CITATION_1] .",
